Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to bring to market for lease 2A Hayes Road, Rosebery.

This 1,025sqm* yard benefits from a prime Rosebery location just metres from The Cannery, Archie Rose Distillery, Messina Gelato and a full list of amenities and transport options into the Sydney CBD and to Port Botany.

Key property highlights include:
-	1,025sqm* regular shaped yard
-	Fully fenced and secure
-	Ideal for parking and container storage
-	Centrally located within Rosebery
-	1.3km* from Green Square Station
-	5.8km* from Sydney CBD
-	8.8km* from Port Botany
-	Available Now

For more inspection, please contact the exclusive CBRE agents.

Presenting a rare and remarkable leasing opportunity, Rosebery’s most historic building has 444sqm remaining on the ground floor of modern character office/showroom space. 
Adaptability is the cornerstone of this building and will appeal to diverse commercial enterprises, from fashion houses, to fin-tech, corporate headquarters to furniture showrooms.
The building has been upgraded to modern standards, retaining the massive timber beams and sandstone façade. Now you can occupy this unique property and take advantage of everything the building and location has to offer.

Features:

•	Character building with high ceilings, exposed timber beams, sandstone walls and original features
•	Ground floor showroom/office space totalling 444sqm*
•	Front and side access for off-street parking for 6 vehicles
•	Great exposure and visibility
•	DDA compliant and wheelchair accessible
•	Concealed underfloor electricals and air-conditioning ducts (fully operational)
•	Exclusive kitchen facilities and restrooms on each floor; ground floor shower facilities
•	850m* to Green Square Station
•	Only 5 minutes* by train to Sydney CBD from Green Square Station
•	Easy motorway access to the Sydney CBD, Eastern Distributor and major arterial roads
